OL,3,CHealer would 'never' persuade someone
OL,4,Cnot to take insulin, court told
OL,6,FAn alternative healer accused of the
OL,7,Fmanslaughter of a diabetic woman who
OL,8,Fstopped taking insulin at one of his
OL,9,Fworkshops has told a court he would
OL,10,F"never" persuade someone who needed
OL,11,Ftheir diabetes medication not to take
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,FDanielle Carr-Gomm, 71, died at Cleeve
OL,15,FHouse in Seend, Wiltshire, where she
OL,16,Fwas taking part in the event in
OL,17,FOctober 2016 which promoted paida
OL,18,Flajin therapy, in which patients are
OL,19,Fslapped, or slap themselves,
OL,20,Frepeatedly.
