OL,3,CHealer would 'never' persuade someone
OL,4,Cnot to take insulin, court told
OL,6,FHongchi Xiao, 61, of Cloudbreak in
OL,7,FCalifornia, who was described as
OL,8,F"Master Xiao" in the programme for the
OL,9,Fevent, is on trial at Winchester Crown
OL,10,FCourt accused of the manslaughter by
OL,11,Fgross negligence of Mrs Carr-Gomm,
OL,12,Ffrom Lewes in East Sussex.
OL,14,FThe court previously heard how Xiao
OL,15,Fsaid "well done" to Mrs Carr-Gomm
OL,16,Fafter she told the group she had
OL,17,Fstopped taking her insulin at the week-
OL,18,Flong retreat, and prosecutors had said
OL,19,FXiao failed to seek medical help for
OL,20,Fher as she became seriously ill.
