OL,3,CHealer would 'never' persuade someone
OL,4,Cnot to take insulin, court told
OL,6,FGiving evidence on Thursday 11 July,
OL,7,Fhe said, when asked if insulin was
OL,8,Fbad: "Of course I would never say it
OL,9,Fis bad, it is useful."
OL,11,FAsked whether if someone needed
OL,12,Finsulin if he would ever try to
OL,13,Fpersuade them not to take it, he
OL,14,Freplied: "Never."
OL,16,FOn his attitude towards medication at
OL,17,Fhis workshops, he added: "First of
OL,18,Fall, I said I'm not a medical doctor,
OL,19,Fso everyone is responsible for their
OL,20,Fown medication.
